---
---
<section class="gap-section" id="gap">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="gap-header reveal">
      <p class="section-tag">The Middle Ground</p>
      <h2 class="section-headline">
        There's a gap between "too expensive" and "too frustrating."<br />
        <em>We fill it.</em>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="gap-grid">
      <!-- DIY -->
      <div class="gap-col muted reveal">
        <svg class="gap-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true">
          <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/>
          <path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/>
          <path d="M7 8l3 3-3 3M13 14h4"/>
        </svg>
        <p class="gap-label">DIY</p>
        <p class="gap-price">$20–30/month</p>
        <ul class="gap-bullets">
          <li>Wrestling with templates</li>
          <li>Hours of your time</li>
          <li>"Who do I call when it breaks?"</li>
          <li>Looks like everyone else's</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Managed (featured) -->
      <div class="gap-col featured reveal">
        <span class="gap-badge">You are here</span>
        <svg class="gap-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
          <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/>
        </svg>
        <p class="gap-label">Managed</p>
        <p class="gap-price">$75/month &middot; $0 upfront</p>
        <ul class="gap-bullets">
          <li>Built for you by a pro</li>
          <li>Unique to your brand</li>
          <li>Real person answers the phone</li>
          <li>Updates included monthly</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Custom -->
      <div class="gap-col muted reveal">
        <svg class="gap-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M12 15a3 3 0 1 0 0-6 3 3 0 0 0 0 6z"/>
          <path d="M19.4 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33 1.82l.06.06a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 2.83l-.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82-.33 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1 1.51V21a2 2 0 0 1-4 0v-.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 19.4a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82.33l-.06.06a2 2 0 0 1-2.83-2.83l.06-.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.68 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51-1H3a2 2 0 0 1 0-4h.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.6 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33-1.82l-.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 2.83-2.83l.06.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 4.68a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1-1.51V3a2 2 0 0 1 4 0v.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1 1.51 1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82-.33l.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 2.83 2.83l-.06.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 19.4 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.51 1H21a2 2 0 0 1 0 4h-.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51 1z"/>
        </svg>
        <p class="gap-label">Custom</p>
        <p class="gap-price">$5,000+ upfront</p>
        <ul class="gap-bullets">
          <li>Bespoke design &amp; code</li>
          <li>Weeks or months to complete</li>
          <li>Ongoing vendor hunting</li>
          <li>Great, if you have the budget</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
